# Copy to `.tizen.env` (git-ignored) and fill in. Used by the Makefile.

# Your TV's IP address (Settings → Network, or the router). Developer Mode must
# be ON (see SETUP.md). Port is 26101 for TV sdb.
TV_IP=192.168.1.50
# TV_PORT=26101

# Name of the signing profile you created in Certificate Manager (SETUP.md).
PROFILE=LUMA

# Only needed if the Tizen CLI isn't on your PATH point at your install:
# TIZEN_HOME=/Users/you/tizen-studio
